## Existing Code Insights

### Reusable Assets
- **Design system (`index.css`):** Complete oklch-based theme with light/dark modes, shadcn token mappings, OJ-specific status/difficulty colors — no changes needed.
- **UI components (`components/ui/`):** Button, Input, Card, Badge, Dialog, Tabs, Table, Separator, Loading, Skeleton, EmptyState, InlineError, ErrorBoundary — all built on shadcn/CVA pattern.
- **Icon library:** Lucide React (`lucide-react`) is the standard. Material Symbols are being phased out.
- **Skeleton components (`components/skeletons/`):** Created in Phase 15 for loading states.

### Established Patterns
- **Semantic tokens:** Use `bg-card`, `text-foreground`, `border-border`, `text-muted-foreground` instead of hardcoded colors.
- **Component imports:** Use `@/components/ui/*` for shared UI primitives.
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4 with `cn()` utility for class merging.
- **Font:** Inter Variable with `cv01`, `ss03` features enabled.
- **PC-only:** 1280px+ responsive, no mobile breakpoints.

### Integration Points
- All changes are frontend-only — no backend modifications needed.
- Changes affect 50+ page files in `frontend/src/pages/`, component files in `frontend/src/components/`, and the CSS theme in `frontend/src/index.css`.
- Build verification: `npm run build` + `npx vitest --run` must pass.

